---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHeader from '../../components/SectionHeader.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="System | ForgeCore"
  description="How ForgeCore discovers opportunity, creates assets, deploys monetization, measures outcomes, and compounds over time."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="reading">
      <SectionHeader
        eyebrow="System"
        title="ForgeCore is a deterministic operating system for autonomous revenue."
        description="It is designed to discover opportunity, convert it into assets, deploy monetization, measure real-world results, and reallocate effort without emotional drift."
      />
      <div class="prose">
        <p>ForgeCore exists to build a resilient financial instrument, not a trend product. It does not depend on one model, one channel, or one monetization tactic. It treats architecture as the durable source of leverage and models as replaceable labor.</p>
        <p>The system is strategy-agnostic, channel-independent, self-documenting, and self-improving. If a channel dies, allocation shifts. If a platform changes, implementation adjusts. If a strategy underperforms, the system prunes it.</p>
        <p><a href="/system/how-it-works">Read how it works</a> or <a href="/system/principles">review the principles</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
